<p class="ql-align-justify">督导小组召开教师座谈会深入了解校园文化</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201202/1ff75b7404674c9384ce8ac001020058.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201202/03199f210c2c49938a7dd8dd7aac9b13.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
